\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32829bcf919ce7d471b29b6ed0d7372cde9dcde","tid":61210,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"關平台上食烏冬<br />\n關羽床上食檸檬"},{"pid":"e8ec5ada0db190c85ed2cbccdee70f72c38a46c0","tid":61210,"uid":48078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:28:49.000Z","msg":"唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d9deba216628d3030582fbab4141a94a79c75e","tid":61210,"uid":36013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"終於唔係撈飯"},{"pid":"ab2ca6e3f993cde0d985e6274d66814fd1b82c3e","tid":61210,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:29:14.000Z","msg":"食多啲新鮮五谷雜良身體先會好 <br />\n栗米 蕃薯"},{"pid":"c6a7512e3ab7d728246d38291b5928423daa8dbd","tid":61210,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又食丸 食得多丸無益</blockquote><br />\n呢個真，不如買啲瘦肉代替丸啦</blockquote><br />\n唔好痴線啦 你估瘦肉又好健康咩 食下丸都話唔好真係上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5967a2b43011eb7b849c3987bfecc406873b1606","tid":61210,"uid":1558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"二哥有無認真考慮下改善平仔啲伙食<br />\n真心麻麻地<br />\n一般黎講細個盡可能接觸多啲款嘅菜同肉先至會令小朋友大個啲咩都食，另一方面營養先均衡<br />\n睇平啲菜多數都係深綠，有啲營養其他瓜菜先有<br />\n<br />\n睇得出二哥錫仔，但要俾多少少花款同埋唔好俾咁多丸佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0443093c602f66c38a86ef35878d114c5ef96b","tid":61210,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關平台上食烏冬<br />\n關羽床上食檸檬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b53d14705b2db94a5a182cc008a72c505a7025","tid":61210,"uid":54173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"未加湯啫<br />\n浸得耐淋哂先唔好食呀"},{"pid":"2488b7a15e1dd92ccd32f46a18ac4196f951fb97","tid":61210,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又食丸 食得多丸無益</blockquote><br />\n呢個真，不如買啲瘦肉代替丸啦</blockquote><br />\n唔好痴線啦 你估瘦肉又好健康咩 食下丸都話唔好真係上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好在今次係我老婆煮既啫"},{"pid":"c3dc63c6b882f839d911e6c6d7255a03d2548daf","tid":61210,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:32:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未加湯啫<br />\n浸得耐淋哂先唔好食呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食先加湯<br />\n<br />\n聰明也"},{"pid":"b1d8cc1275168c6cd96facb19c94a3a747d17418","tid":61210,"uid":36184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:32:22.000Z","msg":"加d番茄啦"},{"pid":"8e3be745ae186f1c413b8bb543131106a815137f","tid":61210,"uid":8719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"啲膳食好左係咪因為驚佢再入院"},{"pid":"b70febb9ff4138a7b111163ecf1f2c66abe75865","tid":61210,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"平仔食飽d<br />\n將來脫貧就有湯飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62f010a568b91428a309c2bb72bdbdcbe316fba0","tid":61210,"uid":1558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又食丸 食得多丸無益</blockquote><br />\n呢個真，不如買啲瘦肉代替丸啦</blockquote><br />\n唔好痴線啦 你估瘦肉又好健康咩 食下丸都話唔好真係上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肉黎講，瘦肉都唔健康我真係好擔心你仲有咩肉好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737d4f38ed842fbedf32399ef175ddf67ae7ff82","tid":61210,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-3