e":"2016-12-31T05:57:05.000Z","msg":"關平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 湯呢？"},{"pid":"f814a84140757858c19fbcbca541584611373682","tid":61210,"uid":54988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二哥有無認真考慮下改善平仔啲伙食<br />\n真心麻麻地<br />\n一般黎講細個盡可能接觸多啲款嘅菜同肉先至會令小朋友大個啲咩都食，另一方面營養先均衡<br />\n睇平啲菜多數都係深綠，有啲營養其他瓜菜先有<br />\n<br />\n睇得出二哥錫仔，但要俾多少少花款同埋唔好俾咁多丸佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係睇見都唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b6dd9a80bda706804fa1f2127265daed2129ed","tid":61210,"uid":46669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇完二哥既post我終於知d怪獸家長係點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我咁都叫怪獸？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思唔係話二哥你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇左你咁多post唔明點解咁多人屌你餐飯<br />\nbtw建議二哥出post準備定d草同九大簋應付健康撚同狗飯撚"},{"pid":"f82b2fb83e4cefd61f21d5aa1eaec46d5a0e3fec","tid":61210,"uid":18138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:00:43.000Z","msg":"我個外<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61412ace3b1630140d70c9c4ffed6cb9d3e23055","tid":61210,"uid":18138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個外<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個名"},{"pid":"96fe5b7e80f19adce681284da62988d26b2ba3c7","tid":61210,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:01:55.000Z","msg":"平仔咁大個唔好要比咁多爛飯佢食啦，好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/n